title: Derren Brown Audiobooks - Hypnotism, Magic, and Memory
description:
These are a collection of three audio books, written and read aloud by Derren Brown himself. They are from his book "Tricks of the Mind", which I highly recommend.


I am only making these available because if you don't live in the UK, its damn near impossible to get these, as you can only buy them from iTunes UK (or Audible), and I had to jump through a lot of BS to buy these. 


Now then...


SOAPBOX
***If these are available to you to purchase in your country, please do so. Derren Brown is an profound performer who is kind enough to show us how he, and Big Media, messes with our heads, and personally I think he deserves our support. These weren't that expensive, so please buy them if you can. Thank you!**
/SOAPBOX


Enjoy!

P.S. Or if you don't want to deal with DRM bullshit.
